com.jmr.wrapper.client

Class Client

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jmr.wrapper.client.Client
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IProtocol

    public class Client
extends java.lang.Object
implements IProtocol
    Networking Library Client.java Purpose: Starts a connection to a server and manages the TCP and UDP sockets. Provides methods to send packets over UDP and TCP and it also allows a listener to be set to wait for new connections, disconnections, and packets. It also provides a method to set the type of encryption being used if any.
    Version:
    1.0 7/19/2014
    Author:
    Jon R (Baseball435)
